      "title": "Water Cut for several areas in Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A 24-hour water is in effect for Colombo 12, 13, 14 & 15.",
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board said that a low-pressure supply will be experienced in Colombo 1.",
        "It added that repair works are in progress and the Water Board expects to restore supply by 6.00 am on Friday 08th July 2022."
      ],
